trans-unit.source: Encapsulates all Access Control Entry (ACE) types currently defined by Microsoft Corporation.
trans-unit.target: Encapsula todos os tipos ACE (Entrada de Controle de Acesso) atualmente definidos pela Microsoft Corporation.

trans-unit.source: All <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> objects contain a 32-bit access mask and a <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Todos os objetos <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> contêm uma máscara de acesso de 32 bits e um objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the access mask for this <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define a máscara de acesso para esse objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" />.

trans-unit.source: The access mask for this <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> object.
trans-unit.target: A máscara de acesso para este <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> object associated with this <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> associado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> object associated with this <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier" /> objeto associado a esta <see cref="T:System.Security.AccessControl.KnownAce" /> objeto.

trans-unit.source: No restrictions are placed on the <xref:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier> object.
trans-unit.target: Nenhuma restrição é imposta a <xref:System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier> objeto.
